text: Jessica "Jessy" Schram (born 15 January 1986) is an American actress. She played Hannah Griffith in Veronica Mars. She also played Susan Davis in the Jane Doe television series on the Hallmark Channel. Schram was born in Skokie, Illinois. ==References== Category:Actors from Skokie, Illinois Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:1986 births Category:Living people
